data.description: Adorable 3 bed, 1.5 bath home with a bonus room that could be used as an art/music studio, additional bedroom or office.This home has charm, appeal and a sense of open space from the laundry room all the way up to the charming dormer bedrooms. Ductless heat pumps to keep it warm in winter and cool in summer. The kitchen is unique and creative with an open view of the dining and living rooms.The large backyard is just waiting for the outdoor living it was meant to host. New exterior paint.
